    "In addition, businesses can identify potential threats and vulnerabilities by monitoring the dark web for emerging threats and vulnerabilities.",
    "Research question 2: \"How does the commercial sector monitor dark web data with advanced tools and technologies?",
    "\"The research for this question is based on web-based articles.",
